posts.subject: Hello All !
posts.body:
Lets get this on a tray. Nice. 

So hey i first hopped on zero straight after christchurch when my aussie isp started blocking 8ch. Had not been back since. Seems to be working as intended. Good Stuff. 

I was actually keeping a rather cool head by following codemonkey Ron on twatter. I got up thismorning fully expecting 8ch to back up on BitMitigate and i gotta say it was a rude shock to see even they got their hosting pulled. Yep everything is rented. Big suprise. 

Im sure they will be back up eventually but i must say 

- the shooter in elpaso did not feel right 
- the actions of cloud fare did not seem right 
- the wave of comments on 4chan disavowing 8ch and pol and anyone right of centre did not feel organic
- the wave of hate against 8ch did not feel organic 

It all stinks and feels like a targeted surgical military strike. Just my $0.02
